description: Cloud flashcards allows you to get quizzed on questions about using cloud services. The responses are in a user friendly fashion that doesn't make you feel that you got an answer right or wrong, but states the correct answer to the question. For instance, 'The answer is three, a security group'.
exampleInteractions: Alexa, launch Cloud Cards and new game
Alexa, launch Cloud Cards and start game
name: Cloud Cards
shortDescription: Cloud flashcards allows you to get quizzed on questions about using cloud services.
